# Offline-safe builds (fonts)

- Do **not** rely on `next/font/google` in builds that may run without internet access.
- Prefer **system font stacks** (or self-hosted local fonts committed to `public/` / `app/`).
- If typography vars are used in CSS (e.g. `--font-sans` / `--font-mono`), ensure they have sensible **fallbacks**.

